\end{IEEEeqnarray}
Setting $M_n \define  (2a_n+1)/K $, and combining~\eqref{eq: asy-error-eva},~\eqref{asy-secrecy-eva}, and Theorem~\ref{thm:ach-wiretap}, we conclude that
\begin{IEEEeqnarray}{rCl}
