Following similar steps as in the proof of~\cite[Th.~48]{polyanskiy10-05}, and using that $\tilde{P}_X^*$ is the unique maximizer of~\eqref{eq:ub-dmc-secrecy-capacity} and that $\tilde{V}(\tilde{P}_X^*,P_{YZ|X})>0$, we obtain  
\begin{IEEEeqnarray}{rCl}
