\label{eq:expand-gamma'-conv-dmc}
\end{IEEEeqnarray}
Finally, setting~$\gamma = \|\setX\|\log(n+1) + \gamma'(1-{\epsilon}-{\delta}-\tau)$ and $\tau =1/\sqrt{n}$, and using~\eqref{eq:expand-gamma'-conv-dmc},~\eqref{eq:bound-PYZ}, and~\eqref{eq:bound-idcdf-conv-2}, we conclude the proof of~\eqref{eq:eq:thm-conv-expansion}.






